fields.description:
h3. Notify the repositories to be added on Jira when not automatically set to do so.
h3. Display a message on the UI when there are repositories to be added to Jira. For example: 
{panel:borderStyle=solid|borderColor=#6A8EB3 |bgColor=#F8F8F8}
# You've created a new repository on Github/Bitbucket.
# When you access *Jira* > *Settings* > *Applications* > *DVCS accounts* Jira should notice that you have 1 new repository to be added to your list. 
{panel}
